## Then Deploy on Vercel

1. Go to **vercel.com** → Sign in with GitHub
2. Click **"Add New Project"**
3. Find `coreinventory1` → click **"Import"**
4. You will see a configuration screen — set these:

| Field | Value |
|---|---|
| **Root Directory** | `frontend` |
| **Framework Preset** | `Vite` |
| **Build Command** | `npm run build` |
| **Output Directory** | `dist` |

5. Click **"Deploy"**
6. Wait 2 minutes → you get a live URL like `https://coreinventory1.vercel.app`

